# Maintainer-owned paths. GitHub requests review from these owners on any PR
# touching them; .github/workflows/sensitive-paths-guard.yml additionally
# HARD-FAILS a non-maintainer PR that edits them (this file alone only
# requests review -- the workflow is the real enforcement).
#
# Why these specific paths (see docs/sn74-emission-strategy.md,
# docs/testing-strategy.md): the scoring harness, the governance/CI
# machinery that protects it, the strategy docs defining the rollout, and
# the dashboard's bot-written data feed are the parts a miner PR must never
# be able to quietly rewrite in the course of "just adding a transform".

/eval/                    @zeokin
/docs/                    @zeokin
/.github/                 @zeokin
/dashboard/data.json      @zeokin
